    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/credibility-assessment-team-nagaraja",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed the required level. The single gap (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is accepted on the basis that the single-condition ASTM F1717 protocol is the regulatory standard for this device class and that the model risk level 3 is adequately offset by the direct validation evidence. All three QoIs satisfy both quantitative acceptance criteria. The overall credibility package is accepted for submission.",
